            . I am a constable. About half-past seven o'clock in the morning I heard the alarm, and picked up the parcel - in a few minutes after the prisoner was brought to me.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. It was dark. I heard the alarm, ran after the man, and they stopped me.</p>
